{"tid":2088711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致咁多位真香港人，認清目標，不打陣地戰","createTime":"2020-07-01T09:32:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T11:28:27.000Z","uid":38177,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a971dd3f4c25616caa4253dca127f62a39612eaf","tid":2088711,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T09:32:44.000Z","msg":"多謝咁多位真香港人，喺國安法的陰霾下<br />\n<br />\n好多人都自我捆綁<br />\n有錢既，有樓既，會驚沒收經營多年既財產<br />\n年輕既，怕斷送自身前途<br />\n年老既，亦有好多負擔同包袱<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊類人，今日有出黎，都係真香港人<br />\n因為明白到，今時今日政府管治下，呼吸都有罪，即使你係路人，都可能被打，被拘捕，被失蹤，所以多謝你地<br />\n<br />\n今日現在好多唔同類型既人，有示威者，有和理非，有勇武，有路人，發揮唔同作用<br />\n每個人都有自己目標<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">達成目標後，唔好打陣地戰，「只需要，死不去」咁先有未來</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">再一次多謝咁多位真香港人</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">可以再見到你哋一次真係好開心</span></span>"},{"pid":"34e2b67607da5fa3c3326c7180017c01089c4811","tid":2088711,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T09:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b654f0ff0629ea6fd034e7a092d706c874a5755","tid":2088711,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T09:34:06.000Z","msg":"2020.7.1 港島開始多人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2088024\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2088024</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n邊個話冇人 有圖有真相"},{"pid":"9bac48819e141f64c37ac7779fee8f3c3a4327a6","tid":2088711,"uid":27530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T09:34:26.000Z","msg":"我覺得呢一刻只可打社交戰"},{"pid":"746edb16f9e3817f6da1433f519a312d67759856","tid":2088711,"uid":173227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bac48819e141f64c37ac7779fee8f3c3a4327a6","tid":2088711,"uid":27530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T09:34:26.000Z","msg":"我覺得呢一刻只可打社交戰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01